ALL CONTENT GENERATED BY AI, EXCEPT THE LICENSE FILE.


How to use it

  Start with the orchestrator. It delegates to the pipeline when needed.

  Commands:

     Claude Code    /prompt-architect
                    /prompt-architect-planner
                    /prompt-architect-builder
                    /prompt-architect-reviewer

     OpenCode       @prompt-architect
                    @prompt-architect-planner
                    @prompt-architect-builder
                    @prompt-architect-reviewer

  Pipeline flow (when creating a new agent):
     1. Planner — Discovery & Architecture
     2. Builder — Writes the system prompt
     3. Reviewer — Tests and evaluates

  Quick edits? Use `/prompt-architect` directly.


